2009-04-XX -- Version 0.0.1
 * Laid down the basics of the REST API
 * DirectoryResource, a read-only resource providing access to files
 * Basic internal asynchronous HTTP server which supports:
   * Main request methods (GET and POST tested)
   * Query strings (GET request parameters)
   * POST application/x-www-form-urlencoded form data
   * Content negotiation
 * Router class to route requests to other Resource(s) based on URI path
 * Three ready-to-try examples
 * A comprehensive documentation

This release was brought you by:
    Lorenzo Villani
    Michael Howell
